procedure.description:
[cacheRetention — Complementary Optimization] Before compression runs, enable **prompt caching** for a 90% discount on cached tokens:

```json
{
  "models": {
    "model-name": {
      "cacheRetention": "long"
    }
  }
}
```

Compression reduces token count, caching reduces cost-per-token. Together: 50% compression + 90% cache discount = **95% effective cost reduction**.
